Package edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    The Animal object represents a general way to keep track of the animals that come to our veterinary office.
    AnimalNameComparator
    This object is a comparator, that will compare Animals by their name.
    AnimalOwnerComparator
    This object is a comparator, that will compare Animals by their Owner's name.
    Appointment
    The Appointment object is made to keep track of the appointments set up in the vet office.
    AppointmentAnimKindComparator
    This object is a comparator, that will compare Appointments by their Animal Kind.
    AppointmentDateComparator
    This object is a comparator, that will compare Appointments by their date.
    AppointmentOwnerComparator
    This object is a comparator, that will compare Appointments by their Owner's name.
    Bird
    The Bird object is a subclass of Animal, so it will inherit all of it's fields and methods.
    Disease
    Disease conatains the diseases that the animals might have.
    Dog
    The Dog object is a subclass of Animal, so it will inherit all of it's fields and methods.
    Fish
    The Fish object is a subclass of Animal, so it will inherit all of it's fields and methods.
    Owner
    This is an object representing a human who is the owner of a pet or pets who come to this Veterinary office.
    Save
    This is the save class, which will save the animal list and the appointment list, so that they can be retrieved from a file later.
    Vet
